{"tid":586888,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"費Sir傳短訊撐雲加","createTime":"2018-03-10T03:14:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T08:29:30.000Z","uid":4661,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f8c93d61663f55193aa411e177edd8ec46f13b1a","tid":586888,"uid":4661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T03:14:00.000Z","msg":"好毒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images-sports.now.com/sport/news/1/841/20644655841/20652737987_600x398.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-sports.now.com%2Fsport%2Fnews%2F1%2F841%2F20644655841%2F20652737987_600x398.jpg&h=610d9fed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=w%2FJJPWM%2FuT9sStkqp369R2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=0d1aa49c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】備受下台壓力的阿仙奴領隊雲加透露，獲得前曼聯主帥費格遜傳短訊支持。<br />\n<br />\n「我收到很多訊息，很感激。在過去及現在，我跟費格遜的關係都很好，當事情不好的時候，他都會傳短訊給我。」雲加（Arsene Wenger）在費格遜退休前，一直於英超鬥生鬥死，但二人識英雄重英雄。<br />\n<br />\n「我一直都支持所有領隊。在足球裡你沒可能不捱苦，但尋找解決方法卻是一件有趣的事。當你是年輕領隊，就會認為自己可以勝出每場比賽，但事實並不如此，當你從失望中生還，就能夠成為一名更好的領隊。」雲加續說。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴早前4連敗，現於英超排第6，比第4位的熱刺少13分，幸好周中於歐霸盃16強次回合作客以2:0擊敗AC米蘭止血，亦令雲加的壓力稍減。他認為：「我身邊一直都有很多具天份的人，他們都願意為阿仙奴奉獻生命。」"},{"pid":"71582264339d24dd3008d30da2ddb361ab86c979","tid":586888,"uid":128565,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T07:22:06.000Z","msg":"費蛇都迷雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 反雲肯收皮未"},{"pid":"1bd707675cda6112a7b89395e156930cd8e51571","tid":586888,"uid":76412,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T07:32:22.000Z","msg":"為左自己隊波着想姐 根本全英超19隊都想雲爺爺繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c84199eb0a29370b91e96a5198f38609775cc5e","tid":5